<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
You will want some skill in archery for pulling, but that's about all you'll ever use it for.  It's a lot safer to tag a mob from a distance than to run up to it, but you won't be doing much bow-kiting as a warrior.<P>I'd suggest getting the longest-range bow you can, and getting your fletching up to about 56 - that's where damage 1/range 150 arrows are trivial, which is all you'll ever need to pull with.<BR>
</FONT>
