Thankyou for your comments!  I've tried pulling with a bow the last few days and it's worked great.  With a 100 range bow and SOW i've been able to get 2-3 shots off on the incoming MOB. Not to mention no free "pulling" damage taken from MOB. Not much in the way of damage yet, but every point counts so i'll continue using it.
